FBIS3-23173 "jptot010__l94136" JPRS-TOT-94-010-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 10 March 1994 WEST EUROPE FRANCE MP Shot Dead by Two Men Riding Motorbike UDF-PR Deputy Shot in Hyeres LD2502211094 Paris France-Info Radio in French 2045 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502211094 Paris France-Info Radio Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] The UDF-PR [Union for French Democracy] deputy for the Var department, Mrs. Yann Piat, has just been murdered. The former Front National [as heard] deputy was shot dead at around 1930 GMT in Hyeres, two men riding a motorbike opened fire on Yann Piat. [see SELECTED VIDEO REPORTS in the front of this Terrorism Report for TV coverage of this incident]
